data.description: From the cozy front porch swing to the inviting 2 story foyer and open floor plan this Cape Cod style home is waiting for you. The many features include an open floor plan, Master on Main, Large Family Room with Vaulted Ceilings, seperate Dining area, Loft area, Large Bonus room Upstairs converted to a bedroom, a huge finished basement with 2 bedrooms,a large bathroom,rec room,setting room, office and Nursery. The Kitchen has a large Pantry, solid surface countertops, SS appliances with a gas stove and a Screened Porch off the Kitchen that's great for that morning coffee and a good book. The outside has a firepit for these cool fall mornings or you can have your marshmellow roast with the family. The 1.76 acre lot includes a stream bordering on the rear and total wooded privacy. If your looking for a large home with a large lot, this is a must see. No HOA
